<div class="comment" id="comment6139">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20100610210007/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/685/" target="_top">Nemo</a><a href="/web/20100610210007/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100610210007im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20100610210007/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/6139/">#6139</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2008/04/04 16:10 GMT"));</script><noscript>2008/04/04 16:10 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20100610210007/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/c/">
	  C
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #ffffff;">0/0=0.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  <pre class='compact'>C / OpenMP で。
Fortran 版とほぼ同じ。
19行でスレッド8本を生成、
23行で空きスレッドに仕事を割り当て、
28行でスレッド終了待ち

</pre>
	</div>
	
	
	
